In the bomb binary on the laurie account we can see the function "secret_phase", after some checks we deduce that we need to write "austinpowers" after the "9" of the third step ->
	Public speaking is very easy.
	1 2 6 24 120 720
	1 b 214
	9 austinpowers
	opekmq
	4 2 6 3 1 5
->
	Curses, you've found the secret phase!
	But finding it and solving it are quite different...

In the code the first condition told us that we need a value between 1 and 1001. That's only 1000 possibilities so we lockpick this with a little python script.
Result -> 1001
	Wow! You've defused the secret stage!
	Congratulations! You've defused the bomb!